<tr><td>✔ Workspace-wide Q&A eliminates manual searching</td><td>✘ No built-in native calendar or scheduling</td></tr>
<tr><td>✔ Excellent AI writing, summarization, and database generation</td><td>✘ AI project management features less mature than ClickUp</td></tr>
