<h2>2. ClickUp — 📋 Best for Project Management</h2>
<p>ClickUp is the most comprehensive AI-powered productivity platform on the market. It combines AI task automation, customizable project views (Board, Gantt, Mind Map, Timeline, and more), AI writing assistance, time tracking, and over 1,000 integrations into one unified workspace. The AI features are woven throughout the platform — from generating task descriptions and summarizing project status to automatically assigning work based on team capacity. ClickUp's Free Forever plan is one of the most generous in the industry, making it accessible to teams of any size. The 2026 updates introduced ClickUp Brain — an AI assistant that understands your project context, answers natural language questions about project status, and proactively suggests workflow optimizations.</p>

