<p><strong>Workflow tested:</strong> "Set up a marketing campaign with 12 tasks, 4 assignees, dependencies, and a Gantt timeline. Auto-generate task descriptions and a status summary."</p>
<ul>
<li>AI task generation: 9/10 — accurate descriptions and subtasks from prompts</li>
<li>Project view variety: 10/10 — 15+ views including Mind Map and Timeline</li>
<li>Automation rules: 9/10 — powerful triggers and conditional logic</li>
<li>ClickUp Brain accuracy: 9/10 — intelligent Q&A about projects</li>
<li>Integration breadth: 9.5/10 — 1,000+ native integrations</li>
