<p>Gamma is an AI-powered presentation platform that generates beautiful, professional decks from a simple prompt. Type in your topic, choose a template, and Gamma produces a fully designed presentation with text, images, and layout in seconds. It supports real-time collaboration, embedded media (videos, charts, interactive elements), and exports to PDF and PPTX. The design quality is consistently impressive — layouts are modern, typography is tasteful, and the AI makes smart decisions about how to structure your content. For quick presentations, pitch decks, and internal updates, Gamma saves hours of design and formatting work. The 2026 update added AI-driven slide suggestions, brand kit support, and deeper analytics on audience engagement.</p>

